# Email Configuration for Contact Form

# Option 1: Web3Forms (Recommended - Free and Easy)
WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=your-web3forms-access-key

# Option 2: Gmail Configuration (Alternative)
GMAIL_USER=your-gmail@gmail.com
GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD=your-app-password

# Instructions for Web3Forms (Recommended):
# 1. Go to https://web3forms.com
# 2. Sign up for free
# 3. Create a new form
# 4. Copy your access key
# 5. Set WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY to your access key
# 6. Rename this file to .env.local

# Instructions for Gmail (Alternative):
# 1. Create a Gmail account or use existing one
# 2. Enable 2-Factor Authentication
# 3. Generate an App Password:
#    - Go to Google Account settings
#    - Security > 2-Step Verification > App passwords
#    - Generate password for "Mail"
# 4. Copy the generated password to GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD
# 5. Set GMAIL_USER to your Gmail address